lyrics:
[verse]
Precious, ithemba elihlaza ezinhliziyweni zabo
Esihlane samawolintshi, uthando lwakha abantwana bakhe abathathu
Ngaphansi kwelanga, bathulula umjuluko wabo emhlabathini
Babhekana nobunzima bempilo, bathola amandla ndawonye

[chorus]
Njengesibhakabhaka esibanzi, nephunga lezimbali zamawolintshi
UPrecious nabantwana bakhe, bahamba ngasemaphusheni abo
Isivuno esimnandi sezithelo, sibondla umndeni wabo
Ukuphila e-Orange Farm, kuyinto enhle kakhulu yothando
